    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I have taken such good care of it, and it is totally spotless inside and out. If you are looking for a ride that is basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
